reviewText: Amar Gamal es una bailarina estupenda y maravillosa profesora, en el dvd expone una coreografa sobre una cancin de Nancy Ajram. La coreografa yo la considero para intermedio-alto. Me encant!
I bought this video for my wife, who is a pro dancer, and she said that it is good and very helpful.

I bought this for a friend and she loves it!  She said it is nice because there is so much material to learn.  The only downside is that it does not detail some of the moves enough...so you have to learn by watching over and over
